trans-unit.source: Specifies the display behaviors that you can apply to the list item contents in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Angir Vis virkemåter som du kan bruke til å vise elementet innhold i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The BulletedListDisplayMode enumeration represents the display behaviors that you can apply to the content of the list items in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList> control.
trans-unit.target: Opplistingen BulletedListDisplayMode representerer Vis virkemåter som du kan bruke til innholdet i listeelementer i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList.DisplayMode%2A> property uses these enumeration values to set the display behavior of the list item content in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList> control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList.DisplayMode%2A>disse nummereringsverdier bruker til å angi virkemåte visning av listen element innhold i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList.DisplayMode%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, if you set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList.DisplayMode%2A> property to the HyperLink value, the content of each list item in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList> control renders as a hyperlink.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du har angitt for eksempel den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList.DisplayMode%2A>til HyperLink-verdi, innhold for hvert element i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList>kontrollen gjengir som en hyperkobling.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList.DisplayMode%2A>

trans-unit.source: The Text value allows you to display the list item content as regular text with no additional functionality.
trans-unit.target: Tekstverdien kan du vise listen over elementet innhold som vanlig tekst med ingen ekstra funksjonalitet.

trans-unit.source: The HyperLink value allows you to display list item content as hyperlinks.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for hyperkoblingen kan du vise listen elementet innhold som hyperkoblinger.

trans-unit.source: When clicked, a hyperlink navigates to a URL.
trans-unit.target: Når du klikker, navigerer en hyperkobling til en URL-adresse.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListItem.Value%2A> property to specify the URL that a hyperlink navigates to.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListItem.Value%2A>til å angi URL-adressen som en hyperkobling navigerer til.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListItem.Value%2A>

trans-unit.source: The LinkButton value allows you to display list item content as link buttons.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for LinkButton kan du vise listen elementet innhold som koblingen knapper.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList.Click?displayProperty=fullName> event to post back to the server when the user clicks a link button.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList.Click?displayProperty=fullName>-hendelsen for å postere på serveren når brukeren klikker en kobling.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList.Click?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Use the event data of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedListEventArgs> class to determine the index of the link button in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList> that the user clicked.
trans-unit.target: Bruk Hendelsesdata for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedListEventArgs>klassen for å finne ut indeksen for knappen kobling i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList>brukeren klikket.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedListEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: Displays the list item content as hyperlinks.
trans-unit.target: Viser listen elementet innhold som hyperkoblinger.

trans-unit.source: Displays the list item content as link buttons.
trans-unit.target: Viser listen elementet innhold som koblingen knapper.

trans-unit.source: Displays the list item content as text.
